title: Bingo - documentary on Bingo players
description: As John Jeffcoat demonstrates in this offbeat documentary, bingo isn&#039;t just for blue-haired old church ladies these days; it&#039;s also for blue-haired drag queens, trendy hipsters, impoverished gambling addicts, and everybody in between. Scenes from the United States, Europe, and the Caribbean&#039;s one-and-only Carnival Cruise Bingo Ship are featured in this illuminating look at a versatile game and its many subcultures.
